TY  - JOUR
T1  - Randomized Replacement Rules which Maximize the Expected Cycle Length of Equipment Subject to Markovian Deterioration
AU  - Kolesar, Peter
Y1  - 1967/07/01
PY  - 1967
DA  - 1967/07/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.13.11.867
DO  - 10.1287/mnsc.13.11.867
