EP  - 912
VL  - 13
IS  - 11
PB  - INFORMS
N2  - An important function which is neither concave nor convex often arises in production and inventory models. This function is herein called piecewise concave and can be considered to be a generalization of the concave function. Essentially it is the maximum of a collection of concave functions. Various properties of piecewise concave functions are explored in this paper. In particular, a theory is developed to locate the point at which such functions are minimized. A short discussion of applications is included.
AB  - An important function which is neither concave nor convex often arises in production and inventory models. This function is herein called piecewise concave and can be considered to be a generalization of the concave function. Essentially it is the maximum of a collection of concave functions. Various properties of piecewise concave functions are explored in this paper. In particular, a theory is developed to locate the point at which such functions are minimized. A short discussion of applications is included.
